        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-28T15:26:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would also rename the function to getTestCommitDetail().  Then you have a more reusable, better named function.\n\nI don\u0027t see \"context\" as a test var, and have been just making a ctx :\u003d context.Background at the top of my test functions. This separation between test data and contexts was handy when I needed to update the contexts to cancel.",
      "parentUuid": "4b577cfc_e01b166b",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 18,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 18,
        "endChar": 16
      },
      "revId": "812cc92c66452d9ab02c710f919521d52e2ec327",
